name: co2-concentration.csv
dataset_description: This dataset contains information about monthly atmospheric CO2 concentration measurements from March 1958 to April 2020. The dataset includes 741 rows and 3 columns. The 'Date' column represents the measurement date, spanning a time range of 62 years and 1 month (22,677 days). The 'CO2' column provides the raw atmospheric CO2 concentration values in parts per million (ppm), with a range from 313.21 ppm to 416.18 ppm, a mean of 355.31 ppm, and a standard deviation of 28.52 ppm. The 'adjusted_CO2' column contains adjusted CO2 concentration values, ranging from 314.44 ppm to 413.35 ppm, with a mean of 355.30 ppm and a standard deviation of 28.44 ppm. There are no categorical columns in this dataset.
